WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 24]

01:46.590 --> 01:47.820
Triple-flower mark?

01:56.840 --> 01:58.100
Li Jie's body

01:58.150 --> 02:00.120
was also transformed from the six-eyed butterfly.

02:00.120 --> 02:02.820
Its strength reached the triple-flower level long ago.

02:03.040 --> 02:05.100
But since he had no sacred power of his own,

02:05.680 --> 02:07.290
the flower mark never appeared.

02:08.000 --> 02:09.130
Now

02:09.150 --> 02:10.570
that my soul

02:10.640 --> 02:12.530
has fused with his body,

02:12.560 --> 02:14.490
the triple-flower mark

02:14.630 --> 02:16.060
naturally reveals itself.

02:17.150 --> 02:18.420
Well?

02:21.280 --> 02:23.210
Do you still think I'm insignificant now?

02:45.710 --> 02:46.490
Just as I thought.

02:47.910 --> 02:49.930
Looks like in all those rewinds,

02:50.030 --> 02:51.340
I never showed you

02:51.340 --> 02:52.530
the triple-flower mark.

02:53.150 --> 02:54.900
That's why you couldn't withstand my strike.

02:56.280 --> 02:57.530
Well?

02:59.030 --> 03:01.250
Do you still think you're a deity now?

03:03.150 --> 03:04.530
What destroys a deity

03:05.400 --> 03:06.530
is not a devil,

03:07.910 --> 03:10.140
but the deity's own arrogance.

03:13.870 --> 03:15.580
Your body has reached its limit.

03:17.080 --> 03:18.210
This is the last rewind.

03:24.960 --> 03:26.460
I fought so hard to get here.

03:27.960 --> 03:29.810
I won't allow myself to lose to you.

04:02.750 --> 04:04.020
This time,

04:05.310 --> 04:06.900
I will succeed.

04:36.120 --> 04:36.930
See?

04:41.040 --> 04:42.180
I succeeded.

04:43.870 --> 04:44.800
Do you know why

04:44.800 --> 04:46.180
I couldn't dodge your blade?

04:47.070 --> 04:49.180
Because I didn't want to.

04:52.310 --> 04:53.010
Break!

04:54.620 --> 04:56.660
♪It's your light, your storms...♪

04:57.830 --> 04:59.540
Dragon hearts as one,

05:00.000 --> 05:01.450
all to source return,

05:02.000 --> 05:03.570
all barriers break.

05:05.340 --> 05:09.380
♪Sailing afar♪

05:33.040 --> 05:33.780
It's raining!

05:42.510 --> 05:43.780
The drought is finally over.

05:44.160 --> 05:45.250
Luo'an is finally saved!

05:55.060 --> 06:01.460
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from...♪

06:01.680 --> 06:02.620
I did it.

06:09.100 --> 06:12.180
♪The white-haired one looks on through tear-blurred eyes...♪

06:13.750 --> 06:14.370
Wu.

06:17.430 --> 06:18.660
Ji.

06:24.310 --> 06:25.450
I did it.

06:35.680 --> 06:36.330
Wu?

07:28.300 --> 07:35.140
♪No pain, no tears, she takes it all in stride♪

07:35.660 --> 07:39.460
♪Facing the light, she's brave inside♪

07:39.900 --> 07:50.340
♪Who remembers dewdrops fade at dawn's light?♪

08:01.800 --> 08:02.620
This is for you.

08:09.950 --> 08:11.860
I'm sorry for staining

08:12.560 --> 08:13.130
your manuscript.

08:19.120 --> 08:19.860
Long,

08:20.190 --> 08:20.620
I...

08:22.120 --> 08:23.220
I promise I'll come back.

08:25.070 --> 08:25.490
Oh, right.

08:26.830 --> 08:27.620
I've asked

08:27.630 --> 08:28.930
my weasel brothers to look after you.

08:30.120 --> 08:31.130
If anyone dares hurt you,

08:31.560 --> 08:32.490
go ask them for help.

08:36.960 --> 08:38.730
I... I want to use this brush

08:39.080 --> 08:40.730
to write your story.

08:40.910 --> 08:42.090
When you come back next time,

08:42.150 --> 08:43.540
I'll... I'll let you read it.

08:46.080 --> 08:46.730
Do you like it?

08:49.360 --> 08:49.690
You...

08:50.150 --> 08:51.260
you didn't make this

08:51.440 --> 08:52.780
with your own fur, did you?

08:55.080 --> 08:55.730
Of course not.

08:57.460 --> 09:04.020
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

09:04.420 --> 09:10.780
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

09:12.220 --> 09:18.740
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

09:19.180 --> 09:24.900
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

09:27.240 --> 09:28.730
I was the one

09:28.840 --> 09:30.780
who forced the rain to fall with demon magic.

09:31.550 --> 09:33.090
Why didn't I die?

09:36.840 --> 09:38.730
Some force even I do not know of

09:39.510 --> 09:40.500
was protecting you.

09:53.000 --> 09:53.810
But Ji Ling...

10:13.750 --> 10:15.540
People rarely get to have it both ways.

10:15.910 --> 10:17.260
He couldn't bear to let you die,

10:17.720 --> 10:19.330
but he also had to destroy Jiu Ying.

10:20.030 --> 10:21.020
Caught in that dilemma,

10:21.120 --> 10:22.380
he suffered deeply.

10:23.390 --> 10:24.900
You destroyed the Dragon Deity's Power

10:25.510 --> 10:27.030
and ruined the mission to which

10:27.030 --> 10:28.020
he'd devoted a century.

10:28.600 --> 10:29.380
And then he watched

10:29.380 --> 10:30.810
your body and spirit vanish.

10:31.670 --> 10:33.140
That overwhelming despair and loneliness

10:33.140 --> 10:34.180
snuffed out the last bit of hope

10:34.180 --> 10:35.540
in his heart.

10:36.790 --> 10:37.780
Thus,

10:38.630 --> 10:40.420
Lonescale consumed him.

10:41.790 --> 10:43.180
Lonescale lied to me.

10:44.240 --> 10:45.090
He said

10:45.550 --> 10:47.210
Ji Ling was a kind person.

10:47.510 --> 10:48.900
He said he chose to help me

10:49.270 --> 10:50.730
because he wanted to save Ji Ling too.

10:52.440 --> 10:54.180
I never thought it'd kill Ji Ling instead.

10:55.670 --> 10:56.660
You underestimated

10:56.660 --> 10:57.900
how much you meant to him.

11:00.080 --> 11:01.300
You wanted him to live

11:01.440 --> 11:02.300
and yourself to die.

11:03.030 --> 11:04.260
He wanted the opposite.

11:05.270 --> 11:06.810
Lonescale can rewind time

11:06.910 --> 11:08.850
and peer into the past and future.

11:09.440 --> 11:11.180
How could he not have known how it would end?

11:11.750 --> 11:13.210
He knew everything all along,

11:13.840 --> 11:15.260
and that was exactly why he chose to help you.

11:16.240 --> 11:17.420
From beginning to end,

11:17.840 --> 11:19.180
he had only one goal:

11:20.510 --> 11:22.060
to consume Ji Ling completely.

11:26.080 --> 11:28.140
I ruined your plan.

11:29.320 --> 11:31.140
You spent over 100 years playing the Dragon Deity,

11:32.000 --> 11:32.780
alone

11:33.750 --> 11:34.500
and in pain,

11:36.550 --> 11:38.690
all just so you could reach that very ending.

11:40.720 --> 11:42.450
But I couldn't stand by and watch you die.

11:43.840 --> 11:46.020
You shouldn't have existed in this world

11:46.750 --> 11:48.180
just to sacrifice yourself.

11:50.240 --> 11:51.660
That would've been too cruel to you.

11:55.550 --> 11:56.500
I never thought

11:59.960 --> 12:01.570
it would turn out like this.

12:10.750 --> 12:11.450
Ji Ling,

12:13.910 --> 12:15.500
can you hear me?

12:16.910 --> 12:18.260
Please wake up.

12:26.870 --> 12:28.090
Back then, I didn't understand

12:30.440 --> 12:31.810
why so many demons wanted

12:33.720 --> 12:34.660
to wear

12:35.870 --> 12:36.850
human skin

12:39.150 --> 12:40.260
and become human.

12:42.270 --> 12:43.570
A demon's tears

12:44.150 --> 12:45.260
are fake.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.930
They cry just to look

12:48.930 --> 12:50.180
more human.

12:51.750 --> 12:52.930
I don't understand

12:53.870 --> 12:54.850
why so many demons

12:55.720 --> 12:56.500
want to wear

12:57.270 --> 12:58.300
human skin

12:59.670 --> 13:01.060
and become human.

13:02.120 --> 13:03.570
But now I do.

13:14.750 --> 13:16.500
I want to be with you

13:19.000 --> 13:20.610
and live as the most ordinary of people,

13:22.910 --> 13:24.180
beginning work at sunrise

13:25.390 --> 13:26.850
and resting at sunset,

13:28.320 --> 13:29.450
walking hand in hand

13:30.630 --> 13:32.020
through the streets,

13:35.440 --> 13:36.610
and falling asleep

13:37.600 --> 13:39.020
in each other's arms at night.

13:57.390 --> 13:58.850
Ji Ling has been consumed by Lonescale

13:59.240 --> 14:00.260
and remains unconscious.

14:01.030 --> 14:03.020
Bai Ze told us to go to Chi Wen in the Dragon Abyss.

14:03.600 --> 14:05.330
He may have a way to save him.

14:07.200 --> 14:09.420
But without the last share of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:09.790 --> 14:10.660
I can't become a dragon.

14:11.790 --> 14:13.090
When I get there,

14:13.670 --> 14:15.690
I don't know how I'll face my brother.

14:24.750 --> 14:26.090
Whether you become a dragon or not,

14:26.480 --> 14:27.450
you are still you,

14:29.600 --> 14:30.540
Wu Shiguang.

14:34.840 --> 14:37.420
You taught me in the Star Stone illusion

14:37.870 --> 14:39.020
that who we are

14:40.320 --> 14:42.690
has nothing to do with background or bloodline.

14:43.440 --> 14:45.020
What matters more is whom we love

14:45.790 --> 14:47.060
and what we choose to protect.

14:49.240 --> 14:50.090
Besides,

14:50.550 --> 14:51.810
fortune and misfortune go hand in hand.

14:52.320 --> 14:54.260
Without the last share of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:54.720 --> 14:56.570
you will no longer be able to kill Chi Wen,

14:57.150 --> 14:58.020
and Jiu Ying

14:58.870 --> 14:59.960
will stop trying

14:59.960 --> 15:01.090
to possess you.

15:03.440 --> 15:04.690
But if I can't become a dragon,

15:05.790 --> 15:07.090
I can't destroy the Oracle Stone.

15:08.200 --> 15:09.500
When the next full moon comes,

15:09.720 --> 15:11.380
you'll be forced back to the Formless Moon.

15:11.510 --> 15:12.060
I'm afraid...

15:12.440 --> 15:13.260
It's all right.

15:14.270 --> 15:15.330
There's still time.

15:17.910 --> 15:18.730
Besides,

15:20.550 --> 15:21.780
I can sever my tail.

15:27.840 --> 15:29.060
That's the worst possible choice.

15:29.240 --> 15:30.060
No, it isn't.

15:32.600 --> 15:34.060
I'm not like Xiaowei.

15:36.790 --> 15:38.180
I still have you.

15:51.600 --> 15:52.450
What do you

15:53.080 --> 15:54.330
think of this color?

16:00.790 --> 16:01.540
What do you think?

16:06.510 --> 16:08.180
Mortal couples bind strands of their hair together.

16:09.840 --> 16:10.570
At first,

16:11.600 --> 16:13.060
I didn't understand what it meant.

16:14.120 --> 16:15.260
I only wanted a good omen.

16:16.910 --> 16:18.660
But when I braided your hair together

16:18.840 --> 16:19.780
with mine,

16:20.840 --> 16:21.570
I realized

16:22.270 --> 16:23.500
that once hair strands are entwined,

16:24.320 --> 16:25.260
unless they break,

16:26.270 --> 16:26.970
they are

16:28.670 --> 16:29.780
almost impossible to part.

16:31.030 --> 16:31.970
You and I are the same.

16:33.550 --> 16:35.060
We were fated to be entangled long ago.

16:37.240 --> 16:38.810
I will protect you no matter what

16:40.360 --> 16:42.090
and never fail this vow sealed by our bound hair.

17:33.160 --> 17:34.220
You lied to me.

17:39.480 --> 17:40.700
I didn't.

17:41.720 --> 17:42.980
I truly hoped

17:43.550 --> 17:44.610
you'd be able to save him.

17:46.030 --> 17:48.130
What nurtured that dragon scale into a demon

17:49.350 --> 17:51.170
was not only his loneliness

17:52.270 --> 17:53.780
but also his kindness.

17:54.750 --> 17:56.220
Then take me back again.

17:57.200 --> 17:58.130
I want to save him.

18:05.550 --> 18:06.330
It's useless.

18:08.160 --> 18:09.330
He remains unconscious

18:09.960 --> 18:11.460
because his consciousness

18:12.110 --> 18:13.500
has returned to the past.

18:14.880 --> 18:16.170
He's trapped in that part of his past

18:16.240 --> 18:17.610
that came to haunt him.

18:20.590 --> 18:22.300
Haunt him?

18:23.720 --> 18:25.370
It's the old days

18:25.370 --> 18:26.540
before I was born.

18:38.640 --> 18:39.850
Then take me there.

18:41.200 --> 18:42.650
No matter how far back it is,

18:43.880 --> 18:44.940
I'm not afraid.

18:46.590 --> 18:47.650
I can take it.

18:51.960 --> 18:53.500
I know you can.

18:55.720 --> 18:57.220
And I can take you there

18:57.960 --> 18:59.300
so you can see

18:59.960 --> 19:01.740
why he became so lonely.

19:03.750 --> 19:04.500
But...

19:06.030 --> 19:06.780
But what?

19:09.030 --> 19:10.410
But that was

19:10.830 --> 19:12.650
more than 100 years ago.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.980
Far too long ago.

19:16.000 --> 19:18.260
No power can change it.

19:19.270 --> 19:19.890
So

19:20.240 --> 19:21.780
you won't be able to rewind time

19:22.350 --> 19:24.060
again and again like you did before

19:24.680 --> 19:25.780
to alter the past.

19:26.720 --> 19:27.300
Besides,

19:28.160 --> 19:28.890
you

19:29.640 --> 19:30.170
did not

19:31.960 --> 19:32.940
exist there.

19:34.790 --> 19:35.890
Back then,

19:36.240 --> 19:37.330
there was no Lu Wuyi

19:37.790 --> 19:38.850
by Ji Ling's side.

19:39.510 --> 19:40.570
You can only be

19:40.570 --> 19:41.980
a silent observer,

19:42.680 --> 19:44.410
unable to interfere in any way.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.300
Do you still want to go?

19:51.020 --> 19:53.500
♪Don't be sad♪

19:53.500 --> 19:55.220
♪Through every yesterday...♪

19:55.790 --> 19:56.810
This story

19:57.920 --> 19:58.980
is far too long.

20:00.030 --> 20:01.460
Even a day and a night wouldn't be enough.

20:02.310 --> 20:03.540
When we return from Luo'an,

20:04.400 --> 20:05.570
I'll tell it to you slowly.

20:08.380 --> 20:10.940
♪Don't be sad♪

20:10.980 --> 20:12.660
♪Through every lonely night♪

20:12.740 --> 20:15.180
♪Don't you cry♪

20:15.260 --> 20:17.060
♪Through the darkest nights...♪

20:17.440 --> 20:17.980
I do.

20:23.200 --> 20:24.090
I want to know

20:26.960 --> 20:27.980
his past.

20:28.460 --> 20:30.100
♪Through a thousand broken lights♪

20:30.180 --> 20:32.780
♪Don't you cry♪

20:32.780 --> 20:34.380
♪Through every love and every pain♪

20:34.500 --> 20:40.020
♪I'll always stay with you♪

20:40.740 --> 20:42.620
♪Stay with you♪

21:03.510 --> 21:04.130
Yuan Xizai!

21:24.980 --> 21:28.180
[A hundred and fifty years ago]

22:10.550 --> 22:11.170
Xizai.

22:14.110 --> 22:14.880
Xizai?

22:15.750 --> 22:16.520
Xizai!

22:17.280 --> 22:18.130
Xizai.

22:19.440 --> 22:20.020
Xizai!

22:22.030 --> 22:22.610
Save him.

22:23.720 --> 22:24.410
Quick, save him!

22:26.270 --> 22:26.980
Save him!

22:27.020 --> 22:29.220
♪Trapped in this body...♪

22:29.790 --> 22:30.500
Where's your magic?

22:31.590 --> 22:32.540
Why don't you have any magic?

22:33.880 --> 22:34.810
Hurry up and heal him.

22:36.960 --> 22:37.500
Do it!

22:37.920 --> 22:38.500
Hurry!

22:38.640 --> 22:39.410
Save him!

22:40.790 --> 22:41.540
Save him!

22:43.960 --> 22:44.540
Wuhuo...

22:46.220 --> 22:48.660
♪They laugh at me for going mad♪

22:49.100 --> 22:51.900
♪So what if I have?♪

22:52.540 --> 22:55.500
♪Miss me not, miss me not♪

22:55.700 --> 22:58.700
♪When heavy snow falls on the frozen river♪

22:58.900 --> 23:01.260
♪Even the wind will say♪

23:01.660 --> 23:05.540
♪It was never here♪

23:07.460 --> 23:10.660
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

23:10.900 --> 23:13.700
♪To go and see places farther away♪

23:14.140 --> 23:16.860
♪I am not afraid of having no one and no shore♪

23:17.020 --> 23:19.900
♪It is what I willingly choose♪

23:20.380 --> 23:23.180
♪I only need to wipe my tears dry♪

23:23.380 --> 23:26.540
♪No matter how small I am, I can still be brave...♪

23:32.590 --> 23:33.650
Save my brother,

23:34.310 --> 23:35.410
and I'll let you go.

23:40.460 --> 23:46.580
♪Then sink into a sleep as still as jade♪

23:49.400 --> 23:50.890
It's almost New Year's Eve.

23:51.510 --> 23:53.370
Everyone, sort through your things and throw out

23:53.510 --> 23:54.700
what you don't need.

23:55.240 --> 23:56.500
Sweep away the dust and grime,

23:56.880 --> 23:59.300
say goodbye to the old, and welcome the new!

23:59.750 --> 24:00.960
I don't want to see you

24:00.960 --> 24:02.650
live your whole life timid and weak,

24:02.960 --> 24:04.020
bullied by others.

24:04.510 --> 24:06.090
Take the Dragon Marrow

24:06.400 --> 24:07.650
and become

24:08.200 --> 24:09.570
a demon hunter like me.

24:10.270 --> 24:12.300
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

24:12.920 --> 24:14.850
I'm... I'm afraid of demons.

24:19.960 --> 24:20.540
Commander Yuan.

24:20.540 --> 24:23.070
[Ye Daoxuan, attendant]

24:23.070 --> 24:24.700
These were all Xizai's belongings.

24:25.830 --> 24:26.540
Throw them away.

24:28.550 --> 24:29.060
All right.

24:29.720 --> 24:30.890
That might be for the best.

24:37.940 --> 24:41.540
♪As another year comes around, every home is busy getting ready♪

24:41.700 --> 24:44.860
♪Fireworks bloom in the sky♪

24:45.660 --> 24:52.340
♪We softly hum tunes while sweeping every corner♪

24:53.980 --> 24:57.500
♪Window paper-cuts bring peace and joy...♪

25:01.110 --> 25:01.940
Master Daoxuan.

25:03.500 --> 25:08.140
♪May the new year be free of disaster and misfortune♪

25:09.300 --> 25:15.860
♪Fireworks sparkle like stars falling into our eyes♪

25:17.140 --> 25:23.940
♪Snow hangs from the eaves, waiting for swallows to bring back spring♪

25:25.180 --> 25:29.500
♪Another year goes by, and little by little♪

25:29.500 --> 25:32.740
♪Those who've left home have wandered far away♪

25:32.940 --> 25:34.700
♪If only we could go back♪

25:35.180 --> 25:36.620
♪Back to childhood♪

25:37.100 --> 25:40.900
♪Back to the joy that felt whole♪

25:49.440 --> 25:50.330
The New Year's coming.

25:51.160 --> 25:52.330
I've brought you something delicious.

25:53.880 --> 25:55.260
Maybe it'll help you

25:57.350 --> 25:58.740
recover your powers.

26:04.510 --> 26:05.890
Why do you have it?

26:07.400 --> 26:08.170
Let go.

26:08.680 --> 26:09.850
This isn't yours.

26:12.270 --> 26:13.410
It was all your fault.

26:16.160 --> 26:17.850
You wouldn't save my brother,

26:19.160 --> 26:21.130
so he died.

26:22.390 --> 26:23.260
Why?

26:24.030 --> 26:25.130
Why wouldn't you save him?

26:26.680 --> 26:28.060
Since you wouldn't save him,

26:30.590 --> 26:31.850
you can die too!

27:35.020 --> 27:36.580
♪One winter day♪

27:37.580 --> 27:41.740
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes...♪

27:43.750 --> 27:44.500
Wuhuo,

27:45.640 --> 27:46.940
I'm afraid of demons.

27:54.350 --> 27:56.090
What... what kind of demon trick is this?

27:57.400 --> 27:58.370
I didn't do anything.

28:00.070 --> 28:01.500
I don't know any demon tricks.

28:06.070 --> 28:07.740
Did you think that if you took this form,

28:08.270 --> 28:09.810
I wouldn't have the heart to kill you?

28:22.000 --> 28:22.460
Wuhuo!

28:22.590 --> 28:23.090
Take it.

28:23.750 --> 28:24.300
Swallow it!

28:24.300 --> 28:25.020
No!

28:25.350 --> 28:26.090
Swallow it!

28:27.340 --> 28:33.980
♪How deep is the abyss? How heavy is the vow?♪

28:34.420 --> 28:36.740
♪A regret no repentance can erase♪

28:36.820 --> 28:40.780
♪Pressing against an aching heart♪

28:41.380 --> 28:48.740
♪Through countless trials and lifetimes, each of our souls...♪

28:50.880 --> 28:51.780
Give one to Xizai too.

28:51.960 --> 28:52.540
Here.

28:52.750 --> 28:54.020
I've already eaten, Wuhuo.

28:54.110 --> 28:55.020
I don't care.

28:56.000 --> 28:57.260
Mother made them.

28:57.680 --> 28:58.260
Here. Eat one.

28:58.510 --> 28:59.540
I've eaten.

28:59.830 --> 29:00.610
Look how thin you are.

29:00.880 --> 29:01.540
Eat more.

29:01.790 --> 29:02.540
Go on. Eat.

29:03.070 --> 29:03.890
Eat more.

29:04.440 --> 29:05.170
Grow stronger,

29:05.440 --> 29:06.170
just like your brother.

29:08.960 --> 29:09.810
Wuhuo, you're amazing.

29:16.640 --> 29:17.220
Commander Yuan,

29:18.240 --> 29:18.850
I found it.

29:19.960 --> 29:21.570
It turns out the first skin a demon wears

29:21.590 --> 29:22.540
to take human form

29:22.880 --> 29:24.570
uses blood as its medium.

29:27.590 --> 29:28.460
If its blood

29:28.960 --> 29:29.890
stains an object

29:30.480 --> 29:32.090
laden with intense emotion,

29:33.000 --> 29:33.850
the demon

29:33.920 --> 29:35.460
will naturally take on the appearance

29:36.200 --> 29:37.500
of that object's owner.

29:46.790 --> 29:47.460
Commander Yuan,

29:48.960 --> 29:50.330
I thought you were looking up

29:50.350 --> 29:51.740
remedies for the Wasting Sickness.

29:53.030 --> 29:53.980
Turns out it was this.

29:58.880 --> 29:59.700
How have you

30:00.110 --> 30:01.060
been feeling lately?

30:02.070 --> 30:03.570
Who would've thought the Meteor Blast

30:04.000 --> 30:05.410
would cause the Wasting Sickness?

30:09.660 --> 30:16.660
♪Has anyone heard my call?♪

30:20.110 --> 30:21.090
I'm human now.

30:21.090 --> 30:22.780
It's so inconvenient not having claws.

30:23.680 --> 30:25.060
I can't even leave marks.

30:29.700 --> 30:35.660
♪A speck of dust weighs heavy on my heart and throat♪

30:36.540 --> 30:43.580
♪I pace back and forth, counting footprints, too afraid to look up♪

30:43.700 --> 30:50.020
♪Trapped like rainwater in a lake♪

30:50.640 --> 30:51.330
Thank you.

31:12.830 --> 31:14.330
Why do you sound

31:14.830 --> 31:16.090
like you're crying?

31:18.030 --> 31:18.540
Are...

31:19.680 --> 31:21.330
are you sad?

31:24.000 --> 31:25.850
I don't know whether I'm sad

31:29.640 --> 31:30.890
or happy.

31:35.960 --> 31:37.780
I... I think I understand.

31:40.110 --> 31:43.090
Did I become someone

31:45.200 --> 31:46.300
you knew?

31:49.590 --> 31:50.410
Was that person

31:51.720 --> 31:52.980
very important to you?

31:57.240 --> 31:58.130
Father, Mother!

32:03.160 --> 32:03.610
Father!

32:04.550 --> 32:04.980
Father?

32:06.550 --> 32:06.980
Mother...

32:07.350 --> 32:08.260
Wuhuo,

32:10.240 --> 32:11.460
it was the wolf demons.

32:12.440 --> 32:14.650
Take care of your little brother.

32:20.400 --> 32:21.030
And...

32:23.350 --> 32:24.850
don't tell him the truth.

32:25.720 --> 32:28.130
Xizai is timid.

32:34.550 --> 32:35.090
Wuhuo,

32:35.680 --> 32:38.460
why does it smell so strongly of blood?

32:40.920 --> 32:42.300
It was rare for me to come home,

32:43.270 --> 32:44.940
so Father caught two wild chickens

32:45.750 --> 32:48.090
and stewed them for me.

32:48.920 --> 32:50.500
Father, Mother, and I talked it over.

32:52.590 --> 32:54.060
You should take the Dragon Marrow

32:55.440 --> 32:56.540
and become

32:57.200 --> 32:58.370
a demon hunter like me.

32:58.370 --> 32:59.020
No!

33:00.350 --> 33:01.170
Father and Mother

33:01.170 --> 33:02.130
would never agree to it!

33:02.830 --> 33:04.020
Even healthy, strong people

33:04.110 --> 33:05.130
often die

33:05.160 --> 33:06.460
after swallowing Dragon Marrow.

33:06.830 --> 33:07.300
Wuhuo,

33:08.880 --> 33:09.940
I'll die!

33:10.160 --> 33:11.500
Those were greedy fools

33:12.000 --> 33:13.170
who swallowed it recklessly

33:13.200 --> 33:14.260
just to gain sacred power.

33:14.920 --> 33:16.850
The Shilin Sect tested my constitution.

33:17.480 --> 33:18.570
You're like me.

33:20.880 --> 33:21.810
You'll be fine.

33:22.200 --> 33:23.810
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

33:25.790 --> 33:27.060
I'm afraid of demons.

33:27.060 --> 33:28.060
If you're this cowardly,

33:28.720 --> 33:30.300
how will you survive in this chaotic world?

33:32.790 --> 33:34.570
I never wanted to survive.

33:36.240 --> 33:38.330
I've already dragged our family down.

33:39.880 --> 33:40.410
Wuhuo,

33:44.070 --> 33:45.460
just let me die.

33:49.160 --> 33:49.890
All right?

34:12.630 --> 34:13.540
No need to be scared.

34:15.230 --> 34:17.020
They're firecrackers we set off to celebrate

34:17.440 --> 34:18.290
New Year's Eve.

34:20.030 --> 34:20.690
What is

34:21.670 --> 34:22.500
New Year's Eve?

34:25.920 --> 34:26.900
New Year's Eve...

34:30.070 --> 34:31.540
Xizai, do you hear that?

34:31.760 --> 34:33.900
They're setting off firecrackers and doing the dragon dance.

34:35.840 --> 34:36.500
I hear it.

34:36.580 --> 34:42.060
♪We softly hum tunes while sweeping every corner..♪

34:42.070 --> 34:42.730
Look.

34:43.550 --> 34:44.650
How lively it is.

34:44.900 --> 34:48.420
♪Window paper-cuts bring peace and joy...♪

34:52.550 --> 34:53.900
Father, Mother!

34:54.150 --> 34:55.250
Your brother is here.

34:55.320 --> 34:55.820
Wuhuo.

34:55.920 --> 34:57.030
- Father, Mother. - You're here, Wuhuo.

34:57.550 --> 34:58.570
You've grown sturdier.

34:59.230 --> 35:00.380
We missed you.

35:00.380 --> 35:01.130
I missed you too.

35:03.110 --> 35:03.610
Xizai,

35:03.670 --> 35:04.650
you've gotten so tall.

35:05.400 --> 35:06.570
Your mother made dumplings.

35:06.570 --> 35:07.690
Mother made dumplings?

35:07.800 --> 35:08.170
Here.

35:08.290 --> 35:09.820
- Try it. - Eat, Wuhuo.

35:10.000 --> 35:10.980
They're still hot.

35:13.840 --> 35:14.420
Delicious.

35:14.420 --> 35:15.020
You like it?

35:15.840 --> 35:16.690
Give one to Xizai too.

35:17.190 --> 35:18.420
I've already eaten, Wuhuo.

35:18.550 --> 35:19.340
I don't care.

35:19.580 --> 35:20.670
- You're too thin. - I've eaten.

35:20.710 --> 35:21.210
Here.

35:21.670 --> 35:22.210
Eat one.

35:22.550 --> 35:23.380
Go on. Eat.

35:23.860 --> 35:25.620
♪If only we could go back♪

35:26.100 --> 35:27.540
♪Back to childhood♪

35:28.020 --> 35:30.540
♪Back to the joy that felt whole♪

35:30.550 --> 35:31.420
There's plenty more.

35:32.360 --> 35:33.820
New Year's Eve

35:34.710 --> 35:35.860
is the most beautiful

35:37.320 --> 35:38.820
and happiest day in the human world.

35:48.220 --> 35:52.300
♪Who still remembers♪

35:52.780 --> 35:55.820
♪The child I used to be?♪

35:56.260 --> 35:58.020
♪Under the sparks of fireworks♪

35:58.260 --> 35:59.940
♪I gently clasped my hands♪

36:00.260 --> 36:04.980
♪Wishing for a life free of harm♪

36:05.000 --> 36:05.820
Is this for me?

36:07.590 --> 36:08.170
It is.

36:09.360 --> 36:09.940
Eat.

36:11.670 --> 36:12.860
May you be free of misfortune

36:13.960 --> 36:15.210
in the coming year.

36:55.280 --> 36:55.980
Here.

36:56.230 --> 36:57.020
You eat some too.

37:00.920 --> 37:02.460
I've gotten grease all over your hands.

37:03.190 --> 37:03.650
It's all right.

37:04.000 --> 37:05.090
I'll wash them for you.

37:39.920 --> 37:40.650
You're

37:40.960 --> 37:42.290
a little fox.

37:42.920 --> 37:44.130
How can you not have fur?

37:46.150 --> 37:47.090
A bald fox

37:47.320 --> 37:48.860
will get laughed at.

37:49.670 --> 37:51.690
But my eyes can't see,

37:52.760 --> 37:53.610
so I don't know

37:54.150 --> 37:55.770
if I've dressed you up nicely.

37:57.400 --> 37:58.940
As for your blade wound,

37:59.360 --> 38:01.290
I can't mend that yet.

38:02.670 --> 38:03.500
I am

38:03.500 --> 38:04.940
a nameless little fox.

38:05.760 --> 38:07.820
But my little fox

38:08.110 --> 38:09.420
can't go without a name.

38:10.920 --> 38:11.940
Foxes

38:12.710 --> 38:13.820
usually go

38:14.000 --> 38:14.730
"awoo,

38:14.800 --> 38:15.980
awoo."

38:17.070 --> 38:18.820
Why don't I call you

38:19.800 --> 38:20.690
Wu?

38:22.630 --> 38:23.250
Wu!

38:25.960 --> 38:26.540
Awoo!

38:28.580 --> 38:30.100
♪One winter day♪

38:30.540 --> 38:34.700
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes♪

38:34.980 --> 38:41.220
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by...♪

38:41.440 --> 38:42.860
You don't have eyes either?

38:47.660 --> 38:53.620
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart♪

38:54.260 --> 38:55.780
♪In a quiet corner♪

38:56.140 --> 39:00.300
♪Each careful stroke carried a tiny wish♪

39:00.420 --> 39:06.500
♪Lights across the shore, snow trapped his lonely heart♪

39:06.900 --> 39:13.100
♪The moon curved above, a firework lit the sky bright♪

39:13.340 --> 39:19.500
♪He looked up, counting snowflakes, waiting for spring light♪

39:19.700 --> 39:22.380
♪Tears shining in his eyes♪

39:22.460 --> 39:26.100
♪Step by step, he called and cried♪

39:26.500 --> 39:32.180
♪Yet fate fills his bowl of hope with regrets and sighs♪

39:32.460 --> 39:35.700
♪Longing drifts away like threads in the wind♪

39:35.940 --> 39:38.980
♪Like a small boat leaving the shore at night♪

39:39.340 --> 39:45.260
♪The wind takes pity and makes me turn and see♪

39:45.660 --> 39:51.300
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

39:51.740 --> 39:57.900
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

39:58.340 --> 39:59.740
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

39:59.900 --> 40:01.460
♪Bitter and sweet♪

40:01.660 --> 40:04.820
♪The moon stays by my side♪

40:05.260 --> 40:11.060
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

40:18.140 --> 40:23.660
♪The moon accompanies me as I roam the mortal world♪

40:30.900 --> 40:38.420
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

40:57.190 --> 40:58.020
What's wrong?

41:02.070 --> 41:02.730
What's going on?

41:05.760 --> 41:06.290
Hey, stop.

41:08.030 --> 41:09.090
It's all right.

41:17.630 --> 41:18.020
Here.

41:22.960 --> 41:23.420
Calm down.

41:23.800 --> 41:24.650
There, there.

41:26.550 --> 41:27.290
There, there.

41:29.190 --> 41:32.060
I'm in so much pain.

41:33.360 --> 41:34.980
It hurts so much.

41:37.230 --> 41:37.900
Father,

41:38.230 --> 41:39.500
Mother,

41:40.710 --> 41:42.500
take me with you.

41:43.440 --> 41:45.570
Take me with you.

41:46.070 --> 41:46.820
It's all right.

42:48.280 --> 42:48.980
You're awake.

42:49.510 --> 42:50.540
Are you all right now?

43:02.630 --> 43:03.290
What are you doing?

43:04.800 --> 43:05.820
Don't take it away!

43:07.230 --> 43:08.460
It's the only company I have!

43:08.630 --> 43:10.060
Can you give it back to me?

43:10.320 --> 43:11.730
Please give Wu back!

43:14.440 --> 43:15.290
Have you left?

43:49.030 --> 43:50.020
Eyes?

43:55.030 --> 43:56.380
You even stitched up

43:56.920 --> 43:58.060
the torn part.

44:26.190 --> 44:27.610
It's my return gift for last night.

44:30.510 --> 44:32.900
You know how to sew?

44:33.550 --> 44:34.690
My family was poor.

44:36.360 --> 44:37.900
My worn-out clothes would be passed down

44:38.480 --> 44:39.570
to my younger brother.

44:40.280 --> 44:41.460
The same piece of clothing

44:42.190 --> 44:43.770
would get patched over and over again.

44:44.670 --> 44:45.860
I did all the mending.

44:50.440 --> 44:51.210
Then why did you

44:51.960 --> 44:54.060
join the Shilin Sect?

44:55.280 --> 44:56.610
Who took care of your brother?

44:58.030 --> 44:59.290
My parents were poor,

45:00.920 --> 45:01.980
and I couldn't read either.

45:04.800 --> 45:05.690
My brother

45:07.510 --> 45:08.460
was sickly,

45:10.000 --> 45:11.690
and his treatment cost a lot of money.

45:12.880 --> 45:14.590
They said if a Shilin Sect hunter

45:14.590 --> 45:16.060
died fighting demons,

45:16.280 --> 45:17.380
the compensation

45:18.630 --> 45:20.900
would be enough to feed a poor family for ten years.

45:22.030 --> 45:23.060
So I joined.

45:24.760 --> 45:25.770
What a pity.

45:29.030 --> 45:31.130
No amount of money means

45:34.320 --> 45:35.650
anything to me now.

45:37.230 --> 45:39.420
I don't have any family left to care for now.

45:40.070 --> 45:40.570
I...

45:42.190 --> 45:44.380
I didn't mean to let your brother die.

45:45.440 --> 45:47.730
I was just an ordinary fox.

45:48.800 --> 45:50.290
I didn't know any magic at all.

45:51.510 --> 45:53.020
By the time I found you

45:53.030 --> 45:54.380
and your brother,

45:55.480 --> 45:57.070
the power Master Dragon Deity gave me

45:57.070 --> 45:58.540
had already been used up.

46:01.110 --> 46:02.650
I don't have any family either,

46:05.190 --> 46:07.940
but I know losing family

46:09.000 --> 46:10.170
must hurt terribly.

46:14.760 --> 46:16.290
How could you not have any family?

46:18.070 --> 46:18.940
Aren't foxes

46:21.030 --> 46:22.570
born in litters?

46:30.840 --> 46:31.650
Maybe

46:32.000 --> 46:34.130
it was because I was born blind.

46:35.150 --> 46:37.380
My family abandoned me in a cave

46:38.110 --> 46:39.380
and left me to fend for myself.

46:48.280 --> 46:50.020
I couldn't save your brother.

46:52.360 --> 46:54.020
How about I give you another brother?

46:58.880 --> 46:59.570
From now on,

47:01.440 --> 47:02.500
I'll be your younger brother.

47:04.100 --> 47:08.060
♪Pressing against an aching heart♪

47:08.820 --> 47:16.180
♪Through countless trials and lifetimes, each of our souls♪

47:16.580 --> 47:21.900
♪Like waves, never fearing sacrifice♪

47:54.960 --> 47:56.340
The war between humans and demons

47:56.800 --> 47:57.730
is growing worse.

47:58.360 --> 47:59.420
All beings suffer.

48:00.360 --> 48:01.610
To end this war

48:02.030 --> 48:03.380
and restore peace to the world,

48:04.230 --> 48:05.770
there is a mission certain to end in death.

48:07.480 --> 48:08.570
Are you willing to do it?

48:13.880 --> 48:14.820
If you are,

48:16.400 --> 48:17.730
swallow this dragon scale.

48:37.550 --> 48:39.340
I'm already as good as dead.

48:42.400 --> 48:43.690
Of course I'm willing.

49:01.550 --> 49:02.290
What are you doing?

49:11.000 --> 49:12.210
I owe you a life.

49:14.190 --> 49:15.210
I'm paying it back.

49:35.800 --> 49:36.650
It hurts!

50:02.420 --> 50:03.580
♪It's your light♪

50:03.780 --> 50:05.660
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

50:05.820 --> 50:08.940
♪That set the night alight♪

50:09.300 --> 50:15.820
♪And lead me through the fight♪

50:17.580 --> 50:19.460
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

50:19.900 --> 50:24.340
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

50:25.140 --> 50:26.820
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

50:26.980 --> 50:32.380
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

50:33.140 --> 50:38.540
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

50:40.860 --> 50:46.900
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

50:47.860 --> 50:50.020
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

50:50.300 --> 50:55.140
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

50:55.500 --> 50:57.820
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

50:58.020 --> 51:03.100
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

51:03.340 --> 51:05.340
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

51:05.620 --> 51:09.980
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

51:10.980 --> 51:17.940
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

51:34.500 --> 51:37.460
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

51:38.540 --> 51:41.940
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

51:42.740 --> 51:45.260
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

51:45.500 --> 51:48.580
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

51:48.980 --> 51:51.300
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

51:51.820 --> 51:56.220
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

51:56.460 --> 51:58.620
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

51:59.020 --> 52:03.980
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

52:04.220 --> 52:05.380
♪It's your light♪

52:05.580 --> 52:07.420
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

52:07.620 --> 52:10.740
♪That set the night alight♪

52:11.500 --> 52:20.940
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
